
                                     g1sync

g1sync is a tool for synchronizing your newest podcast to your Android phone
(or any othe mobile music player).
g1sync does three things:
 1. Start hpodder for catching your latest podcasts.
 2. Check if all your podcasts fit on your mobile device.
 2a. If not move the oldest podcasts to the archive which is not synced.
 3. Create a playlist for quick access of the newest podcasts.
 4. (not to be forgotten) sync the music to the mobile device.

###########
# Install #
###########

Check all files for UPPERCASE VARIABLES at the top, these are the settings.


